Feature: Search a Product
  Scenario: Search a Product Successfully
    Given I access Petz Homepage
    When I search "Aquário Boyu Curvo 100 187 Litros Preto Champagne" with Magnifier Button
    Then I see the tab title "Aquário Boyu Curvo 100 187 Litros Preto Champagne"
    And I see a list with product "Aquário Boyu Curvo 100 187 Litros Preto Champagne"
    And I click at product "Aquário Boyu Curvo 100 187 Litros Preto Champagne"
    Then show the product name "Aquário Boyu Curvo 100 187 Litros Preto Champagne" and price "R$ 3.199,99"